            <sec>
                <title>Sample description</title>
                <p>We received 84 complete responses from 72 different energy projects: 62 different EU Horizon 2020-funded projects (31% of the stakeholder-engaging EU-funded energy research projects running at the time), and 10 projects with other funding sources. For most projects, we received only one response; for eight projects we received two responses
