            <sec>
                <title>Ethics requirements</title>
                <p>The research has been conducted under the ethics requirements and guidelines of the SENTINEL project (Deliverables 11.1 and 11.2), which follows the guidelines of the European Commission. We have applied an ethically-robust methodology for the data collection and processing in the context of this study, under the guidance of the Institute for Advanced Sustainability Studies (IASS) data protection service. This has been supported by bilateral data protection agreements. The respondents agreed to our data protection standards via a GDPR disclaimer, and by participating in the survey.</p>
